<h2 class="about">Available Data</h2>
<p>Enhance your website with automated data of the following:</p>
<ul >
  <li>Data on 3,000+ LBNL researchers and personnel – <em>Updated daily</em></li>
  <li>Data on over 20,000 LBNL publications – <em>Updated weekly</em></li>
  <li>Manually entered data (e.g., photos, research overview descriptions) - <em>Updated either immediately, or daily</em></li>
</ul>

<div style="width:29%;float:left;">
<p>General (supported in all APIs)</p>
<ul>
    <li>Name</li>
    <li>Photo URL</li>
    <li>School</li>
    <li>Titles</li>
    <li>Email</li>
    <li>Street address (includes lat/lon)</li>
    <li>Telephone and Fax</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div style="width:29%;float:left;padding-right:15px;">	
<p>Research-Related</p>
<ul>
    <li>Narrative</li>
    <li>Top research keywords (based on publications)</li>
    <li>Publications (includes source, title, URL)</li>
    <li>LBNL Co-authors</li>
    <li>Similar researchers at LBNL</li>
    <li>Websites (JSON API only)</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div style="width:29%;float:left;">	
<p>Search (supported in XML API)</p>
<ul>
    <li>Find people by name</li>
    <li>Find people by department</li>
    <li>Find people by faculty rank</li>
</ul>
</div>


